{
  "stem": "942.5",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But the Czechs just kept throwing the bread, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And finally the Nazis, these guards, were starting to shoot at these people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I don't know whether anybody was hurt or not.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But you know, I just remember this incident, you know, that these people came, and-- I mean, you know, I hadn't seen kindness like this from anybody, you know.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And that was really-- it meant something, to see that people were willing to do something like that, even though I wasn't able to get ahold of any of this bread, you see.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, and so we continued.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember going to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is a big city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we finally, we entered Austria, because I remember seeing the signs on the railroad stations.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we arrived in a place called Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The train stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was beginning of February of 1945.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The train stopped on this side at-- of the Danube River.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I could see the railroad bridge across the Danube, you know, and that's quite a bridge, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I couldn't understand why the train did not go across the bridge.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They ordered us to get out of the train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as soon as you get off, you had to line up into columns.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I thought that they were going to kill us, right here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember looking at the Danube.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The water was kind of greenish color, and the ice floe going down towards Hungary.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said, this is it, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But no, they told us to start marching.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we marched across the bridge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I remember going through on those railroad ties.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the rails were damaged.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The bridge was damaged from Allied bombing.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
